speech:
Here are some things to note while you stay in Singapore:

1) You need the approval of the Controller of Work Passes to marry a Singapore citizen or permanent resident (either in Singapore or outside of Singapore). This also applies after a work permit becomes invalid.

2) You must also not become pregnant or give birth in Singapore unless you are married to a Singapore citizen or permanent resident and you have the approval of the Controller of Work Passes. This also applies after a work permit becomes invalid.
